EC2-Elastic Compute Cloud:
  Launch considerations:
    - Name and Tags
    - Application & OS image
    - Instance type & size
    - Key pair
    - Netowrk & Security - VPC, subnet and SG.
    - Storage
    - Placement & Tenancy (Optional)
    - Scripts & Metadata (Optional)
  AMI-Amazon Machine Image:
  Instance families:
    - General purpose
    - Memory optimized
    - Storage optimized
    - Compute optimized
    - Accelerated compute
    - HPC optimized
    

